            "advice": ["Check if your dog is lactose-intolerant before giving dairy products.", "Bananas peels should NOT be given.", "Peanut shells should NOT be given."]
        },
        "fat": {
            "subtitle": "Fat",
            "info": "Provide energy, support cell function, and aid in the absorption of fat-soluble vitamins.",
